# MUI theme contract (exact)

## Required light palette (must match exactly)
- `palette.mode`: `"light"`
- `palette.primary.main`: `#4A4540`
- `palette.secondary.main`: `#EDE8E1`
- `palette.background.default`: `#f6f1ee`
- `palette.background.paper`: `#ffffff`
- `palette.text.primary`: `#4A4540`
- `palette.text.secondary`: `#6B6660`

## Required dark palette (warm, brand-consistent)
- Must provide a dark palette where:
  - Base surfaces are **brown/taupe**, not black/navy
  - `background.default`: `#1A1715`
  - `background.paper`: `#26211D`
  - `text.primary`: `#EEE4DB` (soft off-white, not pure white)
  - `text.secondary`: `#C5B6A7`
  - `divider`: `#3D342D`
  - Primary button family stays brown (`#4A4540` base, lighter hover)
  - Pink accent language remains available via secondary/accent tokens
  - Components remain readable with `CssBaseline`

## Typography (required)
- `typography.fontFamily`: `"'Inter', 'Poppins', 'Assistant', 'Heebo', sans-serif"`
- `typography.h1`: `36px / 700 / lineHeight 1.2`
- `typography.body1`: `16px` and uses muted text tone (do not hardcode hex in components)
- `typography.button`: `textTransform: "none"`, `fontWeight: 500`

## Shape (required)
- `shape.borderRadius`: `16`

## Shadows (required)
- Set `shadows[1]` to soft shadow:
  - Light: `0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05)`
  - Dark: may be stronger but must remain soft (no harsh outlines)

## Direction (required)
- `direction: 'rtl'`

## Never
- Do not use pure black (`#000000`) as dark background color.
- Do not use dark blue/navy as base dark-mode surfaces.
- Do not use pure white text over dark surfaces; prefer soft off-white.

